OL,3,CMetropolitan Police cannot sack
OL,4,Cofficers by removing vetting clearance
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police cannot dismiss
OL,7,Fofficers by removing their vetting
OL,8,Fclearance, the High Court has ruled.
OL,10,FThe decision comes after Sergeant Lino
OL,11,FDi Maria successfully mounted a legal
OL,12,Fchallenge, supported by the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police Federation, after
OL,14,Fhaving his vetting removed over sexual
OL,15,Fassault allegations, which he denies.
