OL,6,FHe was found to have no case to answer
OL,7,Fin respect of misconduct allegations,
OL,8,Fand argued that having his vetting
OL,9,Fremoved without the accusations being
OL,10,Fproved is a breach of his right to a
OL,11,Ffair trial.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police maintained
OL,14,Fthat it would be left in a "hopeless
OL,15,Fposition" if it could not dismiss
OL,16,Fofficers after removing their vetting
OL,17,Fclearance because of allegations of
OL,18,Fsexual or domestic abuse.
