OL,6,FSpeaking today, Met Commissioner Sir
OL,7,FMark Rowley said "Today's ruling on
OL,8,Fthe law has left policing in a
OL,9,Fhopeless position.
OL,11,F"We now have no mechanism to rid the
OL,12,FMet of officers who were not fit to
OL,13,Fhold vetting ` those who cannot be
OL,14,Ftrusted to work with women, or those
OL,15,Fwho cannot be trusted to enter the
OL,16,Fhomes of vulnerable people.
OL,18,F"It is absolutely absurd that we
OL,19,Fcannot lawfully sack them.
OL,26,@oD@ROUsD@AOUzD@AOU
