OL,6,F"This would not be the case in other
OL,7,Fsectors where staff have nothing like
OL,8,Fthe powers comparable to police
OL,9,Fofficers."
OL,11,FConfirming the Metropolitan Police
OL,12,Fwould be seeking leave to appeal, Sir
OL,13,FMark Rowley told reporters: "We are
OL,14,Fseeking leave to appeal the judgment,
OL,15,Fnot just for the Met, but for law
OL,16,Fenforcement nationally, due to the
OL,17,Fprofoundly damaging implications.
