OL,6,F"The judge has identified a clear gap
OL,7,Fin the law, one that we have done our
OL,8,Fbest to bridge, but as the judge has
OL,9,Fsaid, the answer lies in strengthened
OL,10,Fpolice vetting regulations.
OL,12,F"So in repeating the same request for
OL,13,Ftwo-and-a-half years, one echoed by
OL,14,Fthe Casey and Angiolini reviews, I am
OL,15,Fonce again calling on Government today
OL,16,Fto introduce new regulations as a
OL,17,Fmatter of extreme urgency."
