OL,6,FHe told reporters: "Finally,
OL,7,Fregardless of the current legal
OL,8,Fframework, the public of London have
OL,9,Fmy assurance, and that of my
OL,10,Fcolleagues, that Di Maria and those
OL,11,Flike him will not be policing the
OL,12,Fstreets or working alongside other
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,15,F"They will remain on vetting special
OL,16,Fleave ` a ridiculous waste of money,
OL,17,Fbut the least bad option until
OL,18,Fregulations are repaired."
