OL,6,FVetting is a process that anyone
OL,7,Fwanting to work for the Met must pass
OL,8,Fto assess their suiltability.
OL,10,FIt includes a series of background
OL,11,Fchecks to identity a persons
OL,12,Fvulnerability and possible risks of
OL,13,Fcorruption, criminality, or behaviours
OL,14,Fthat could damage trust and confidence
OL,15,Fwithin the force.
OL,17,FOfficers will have to provide personal
OL,18,Fdetails, details of any previous
OL,19,Fconvictions, and potentially finances.
