OL,6,FThat information will then be checked
OL,7,Fagainst criminal, intelligence and
OL,8,Fnational security records and public
OL,9,Frecords.
OL,11,FIf an officer does not pass the
OL,12,Fapproval they were previously allowed
OL,13,Fto be dismissed from the force.
OL,14,FToday's ruling will now mean that can
OL,15,Fno longer happen.
