OL,6,FThey Met says, many people fail the
OL,7,Fvetting process because they withhold
OL,8,Finformation, and more than 100
OL,9,Fofficers and staff have left the force
OL,10,Fafter their vetting was called into
OL,11,Fquestion.
OL,13,FWhat is 'Operation Assure'?
OL,15,F'Operation Assure' is a programme used
OL,16,Fto review the vettings for serving
OL,17,Fofficers and staff who would no longer
OL,18,Fpass the original vetting process.
