OL,3,CMetropolitan Police cannot sack
OL,4,Cofficers by removing vetting clearance
OL,6,FIt provides a pathway for the Met to
OL,7,Ffollow if an officer's basic vetting
OL,8,Fclearance cannot be maintained.
OL,10,FIt can lead to that person being
OL,11,Fdismissed from the Met at a gross
OL,12,Fincompetence hearing - as their
OL,13,Finability to hold vetting clearance
OL,14,Fmakes them 'incompetent' to hold a
OL,15,Frole.
OL,17,FMore than 300 officers and staff have
OL,18,Fbeen referred into the Assure process
OL,19,Fsince it was laucnhed in March 2023.
