OL,3,CMetropolitan Police cannot sack
OL,4,Cofficers by removing vetting clearance
OL,6,F107 members of the force have had
OL,7,Fvetting withdrawn, with 96 leaving the
OL,8,FMet.
OL,10,F82 have had their vetting retained.
OL,12,FIn a ruling on Tuesday, Mrs Justice
OL,13,FLang said: "In my judgment, the
OL,14,Fdefendant's powers do not extend to
OL,15,Fthe dismissal of a police officer by
OL,16,Freason of withdrawal of vetting
OL,17,Fclearance.
OL,26,@uD@LOU
