OL,6,FHowever, Mrs Justice Lang said she did
OL,7,Fnot consider this "fit for purpose",
OL,8,Fadding: "The process deprives the
OL,9,Fofficer of any meaningful opportunity
OL,10,Fto challenge a finding of gross
OL,11,Fincompetence.
OL,13,F"The panel merely confirms a decision
OL,14,Fthat has already been made, by an
OL,15,Finternal vetting
OL,17,Fregime which is not Article 6 (right
OL,18,Fto a fair trial) compliant. Where
OL,19,Fbasic vetting clearance has been
OL,20,Fwithdrawn, the only outcome open to
OL,21,Fthe panel is dismissal."
