OL,6,FMrs Justice Lang continued: "Under
OL,7,Fthis process, the normal safeguards
OL,8,Fafforded... are ineffective.
OL,10,F"These safeguards include a full
OL,11,Fhearing, where evidence will be
OL,12,Fconsidered and witnesses mayJbe
OL,13,Fcalled, in which the panel will
OL,14,Fdetermine whether or not gross
OL,15,Fincompetence has been established.
OL,26,@nD@]OUrD@AOU
