OL,6,F"I have long been clear that there can
OL,7,Fbe no hiding place for those who abuse
OL,8,Ftheir position of trust and authority
OL,9,Fwithin the police. Working alongside
OL,10,Fthe Met Commissioner, I want no let-up
OL,11,Fin the vital work being carried out to
OL,12,Fraise standards and rebuild public
OL,13,Fconfidence in the Met.
OL,15,F"No-one who has failed vetting should
OL,16,Fcontinue to serve in the force and we
OL,17,Fwill work closely with the
OL,18,FCommissioner, the Home Office and
OL,19,Fpartners to assess the implications of
OL,20,Fthis ruling."
