OL,6,FLondon's Independent Victims'
OL,7,FCommissioner Claire Waxman said:
OL,8,F"Today's decision by the court is a
OL,9,Fsignificant blow to the hard work of
OL,10,Fthe Metropolitan Police to root out
OL,11,Fdangerous officers and restore public
OL,12,Ftrust and confidence, and the
OL,13,Fconsequences should concern us all.
OL,15,F"I fear this decision could open the
OL,16,Fgates for those accused of horrific
OL,17,Fcrimes to stay in the police force,
OL,18,Fand should be condemned.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
