OL,6,F"Female police officers deserve the
OL,7,Fright to work in a safe environment
OL,8,Ffree from harassment, and victims and
OL,9,Fthe public should be able to trust the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,F"The Metropolitan Police Federation
OL,13,Fhas failed in its duty to represent
OL,14,Fall its members. Police officers and
OL,15,Fstaff ` particularly women ` have
OL,16,Frightly expressed outrage that their
OL,17,Ffees have been used to reinstate a man
OL,18,Faccused of rape, domestic abuse, and
OL,19,Findecent exposure, and it is frankly
OL,20,Fshameful that the federation has
OL,21,Fchosen to support him.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
