OL,6,F"I am concerned this outcome will put
OL,7,Ffemale officers' safety at risk, as
OL,8,Fwell as that of their colleagues and
OL,9,Fthe public.
OL,11,F"The commissioner has been clear on
OL,12,Fthe powers he needs to root out
OL,13,Fpredatory officers, yet the previous
OL,14,Fgovernment failed to take action.
OL,16,F"It is now imperative that the Home
OL,17,FSecretary swiftly draw up new police
OL,18,Fregulations that ensure the public and
